    public class ReactiveWebServerApplicationContext
extends GenericReactiveWebApplicationContext
    A GenericReactiveWebApplicationContext that can be used to bootstrap itself from a contained ReactiveWebServerFactory bean.

      • getWebServerFactory

        protected ReactiveWebServerFactory getWebServerFactory()
        Return the ReactiveWebServerFactory that should be used to create the reactive web server. By default this method searches for a suitable bean in the context itself.
